1. FREE USAGE

PanelIyagi may be used free of charge for personal,
commercial, educational, governmental, and organizational use.

No payment or commercial agreement is required.

------------------------------------------------------------

2. SOFTWARE ARCHITECTURE AND LICENSING

The PanelIyagi core application, including the Qt6 panel,
D-Bus engine service, and related executable components,
is proprietary software distributed in binary form only.

The GNOME Shell extension component is distributed separately
under its own open-source license (GPL-2.0-or-later).

Use, modification, and redistribution of the extension must
follow the terms of its open-source license.

The proprietary licensing of the PanelIyagi core is not
affected by the open-source licensing of the extension.

